Package frclib.vision

Class FrcOpenCvDetector

java.lang.Object
trclib.vision.TrcOpenCvDetector
frclib.vision.FrcOpenCvDetector
All Implemented Interfaces:
TrcVideoSource<org.opencv.core.Mat>, TrcVisionProcessor<org.opencv.core.Mat,TrcOpenCvDetector.DetectedObject<?>>
public class FrcOpenCvDetector extends TrcOpenCvDetector
This class implements a platform dependent OpenCV detector. It implements the TrcVisionProcessor interface which provides methods to use platform specific OpenCV to grab a frame, and output annotated frame to the output video stream.
